<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.2">
<l>cīṟṟa muḷavā kiluñcep puvaṉmakkaḷ</l>
<l>tōṟṟak kuḻitōṟ ṟuvippāy koleṉṟañci</l>
<l>kāṟṟat tiṭaippaṭ ṭakala varmaṉampōl</l>
<l>āṟṟat tuḷaṅkā niṟpaṉā ḻivalavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if there is anger, I will speak up:</l>
<l>Fearing, ‘Will you make me be created again</l>
<l rend="indent">in the pit which creates children?’</l>
<l>Like the mind of a sailor caught in the wind,</l>
<l>I keep shaking intensely, expert with the discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
